    <item>
      <title>莫迪在白宫峰会上寻求避开特朗普的贸易愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/modi-seeks-to-dodge-trump-s-trade-wrath-in-white-house-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五年前，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪最后一次与唐纳德·特朗普总统会面时，这位美国领导人站在莫迪的家乡古吉拉特邦10万欢呼的印度民众面前宣称：“美国永远是印度人民忠实的朋友。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/modi-seeks-to-dodge-trump-s-trade-wrath-in-white-house-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 13:00:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班在选举前削弱德国极右翼防火墙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/orban-chips-away-at-germany-s-far-right-firewall-before-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班 (Viktor Orban) 在布达佩斯接待了德国大选领先候选人选择党，这进一步表明，在本月提前全国选举之前，柏林围绕极右翼政党建立的防火墙正面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/orban-chips-away-at-germany-s-far-right-firewall-before-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 12:20:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约在等待赫格塞特之际大力宣传欧洲在乌克兰的支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/nato-touts-european-spending-on-ukraine-as-it-braces-for-hegseth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲北约成员国即将会见新任美国国防部长皮特·赫格塞斯，他们旨在向特朗普政府展示其对乌克兰提供的全部财政支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/nato-touts-european-spending-on-ukraine-as-it-braces-for-hegseth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 11:57:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克里姆林宫称美国将根据与特朗普达成的协议释放一名俄罗斯囚犯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/kremlin-says-us-to-free-a-russian-prisoner-under-deal-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫表示，根据与唐纳德·特朗普总统达成的协议，预计被关押在美国的俄罗斯人将获释。此前，俄罗斯释放了美国学校教师马克·福格尔 (Marc Fogel)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/kremlin-says-us-to-free-a-russian-prisoner-under-deal-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 11:53:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普顾问希望将美国对外援助转移至华尔街盟友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-advisers-look-to-shift-us-foreign-aid-to-wall-street-ally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普的顾问们已经讨论了将数十亿美元的资金从美国国际开发署转移到一个政府运营的机构，该机构将由阿波罗全球管理公司联合创始人莱昂·布莱克的儿子担任负责人，这是美国对国际经济实力实施改革的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-advisers-look-to-shift-us-foreign-aid-to-wall-street-ally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦肯锡倡导多元化，而竞争对手却放弃目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/mckinsey-strikes-defiant-tone-on-diversity-while-rivals-balk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令政府敦促私营企业放弃公平和包容政策，但麦肯锡公司仍承诺优先考虑员工队伍的多元化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/mckinsey-strikes-defiant-tone-on-diversity-while-rivals-balk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 09:10:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱沙尼亚报告称普京坚持撤出北约的目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/putin-sticks-with-goal-to-roll-back-nato-estonian-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱沙尼亚对外情报机构在年度报告中警告说，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在全面入侵乌克兰三年后，并没有放弃重新划分欧洲力量平衡的更广泛目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/putin-sticks-with-goal-to-roll-back-nato-estonian-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 09:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国加强小船难民入籍规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/uk-toughens-rules-on-small-boat-refugees-claiming-citizenship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府继续严厉打击移民，并收紧规定，防止乘坐小船抵达的难民申请公民身份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/uk-toughens-rules-on-small-boat-refugees-claiming-citizenship</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 08:08:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lutnick 正在探索“贸易工具”以针对欧盟的 ESG 规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/lutnick-is-exploring-trade-tools-to-target-europe-s-esg-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普提名的商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克 (Howard Lutnick) 表示，美国可能会使用“贸易工具”来报复影响美国公司的欧洲 ESG 法规。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/lutnick-is-exploring-trade-tools-to-target-europe-s-esg-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 19:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
